            "content": "After lunch we get into cementing everything in words and that takes us through to about 5pm. I say my farewell and drive through the suburban streets back to Jordan’s house. It’s Spaghetti Bolognaise time! And I get the bottle of wine out of the car that has been subjected to temperature variations that no wine should ever go through. ",
