          "text": {
            "content": "When the Bolognaise is made and reducing we have a bath and reflect on all the lovely holidays that the two of us have gone on together. And, just like that - we’re starving. Nikita arrives home at the perfect time and we all enjoy a pretty incredible dinner.",
